{
  "stem": "25639.4",
  "chunk_idx": 10,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 11.6,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 45,
      "text": "And in about 20 minutes or so, here she comes, and here she is holding a bunch of stuff in her arms, smiling, and laughing.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 46,
      "text": "And I couldn't believe it.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 47,
      "text": "Food.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 48,
      "text": "She was taken to a place-- I don't know where there was such a place in Auschwitz.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 49,
      "text": "We never saw it.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 50,
      "text": "And she was given soda water and herring and something else-- cheese.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 51,
      "text": "And I don't know what else.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 52,
      "text": "Bread.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And she-- she had to carry it like this in her arms.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Where did you get that, mother said.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "She says there's a little canteen down the road for the SS.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And-- and then he just took everything he saw, and he-- until there was no more room in my arms.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And can you imagine?",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "In the meantime, we lost quite a few women among the rest of us, who were taken away because our-- because their strip was not as long as my sister's.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So they pulled all sorts of stunts to thin us out.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "For example, periodically, Dr.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Mengele would appear, and we would have to-- on the pretext of a medical check up-- we would have to remove all our clothes, and in our birthday suits, just sometimes we were asked to turn around.",
      "word_count": 37
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And before you were sent either this way or that way.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And one of those-- he decided who should live and who should die, who is no longer in-- in a shape to go on, just based on what he saw from this selection.",
      "word_count": 33
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Well, one time I was picked out and sent to the infirmary, because there were some what looked like rashes under my pubic hair.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Well, it was in the summer.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "I don't know which month it was, but it was very, very hot.",
      "word_count": 13
    }
  ],
